Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大户爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这种地方干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,散步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这么晚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,梦不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现实才更好？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次免费
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,下次把钱包带来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心  你肯定喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟这扭蛋很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,特别？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,里面装着你想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有什么想要的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,别骗人了  当然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是该冷藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但要是还活着  是不是应该保温才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  说不定会把它煮熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,它能打破吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说  我可以打破它吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把包放下  你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,老地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,爱！老师来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大户妈妈  不用勉强叫她起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来送这周的讲义的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:26.69,Top,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.31,Top,,0,0,0,,总是麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.94,Top,,0,0,0,,没有没有  不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:33.44,Top,,0,0,0,,我只是回家路上来看看罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,里面是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明天再去那里看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我会在学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不搞大点她不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,诶…  那就再多加点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哦？你还说是我做得过火呢  你个魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,给在学校的各位提问：
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要是班上有人被欺凌该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没错！正确答案当然是视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大户爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,打破蛋  把蛋打破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是奇妙蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快点打破它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这很硬  我打不破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快点打破！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,打破！打破它！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你这不是做得挺好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  为什么要在这种地方打破啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是完事了  就出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也不需要用这种口气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,高高在上让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,用普通的语气不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说我也应声了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要跑咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:25.93,Default,,800,0,0,,那个… 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:25.93,Default,,0,800,0,,要快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,它们就是「视而不见」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是肝脏？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是梦  一场噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看看你的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的伤口不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对你来说这是个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但对我来说这是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,总之  在打铃之前我们要一直跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,它们只追我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再说了你在这个世界是不死身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你的眼睛和心脏没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那还叫不死身吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌  为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你买了蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我没买
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,说是第一个免费
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是么  没什么比免费更贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你没有朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不是没有  是不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就不会打破蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不过表面朋友也是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,「是啊是啊」「我知道」「好可爱」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只会这样附和的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我没有挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,现在回想起来  挚友真的很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,男朋友会分手  但挚友是一辈子的事对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你有过男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我先问的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们「一二」一起说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你耍赖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,错的是它们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的  它们不来追我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不来追我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫长濑小糸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那长濑同学就坐大户同学的旁边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起回家吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,「诶」是什么反应啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,太伤人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这里这么清静  是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大户同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我在一起不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是丑女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不丑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛又大又圆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你的发型？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要遮住这边？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的伞呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你的包呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,爱  你朋友来找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是我朋友  我没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我把你忘记的东西送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,双眼虹膜颜色不一样  这叫做异色瞳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在猫和狗之中比较常见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得没必要藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道我因此受欺凌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来都是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,做挚友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是不行…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能做挚友  我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我辜负了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是我交到的第一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就差一点  就差一点就要打铃了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,人行横道  即使和人群一起过也很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再视而不见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经怒不可遏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫西城胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,大户爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爱… 该告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要忘记我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,得救的就只有你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你得打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想把挚友找回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有点温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我保护了胡桃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  要是我保护更多的人  小糸就能复活吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,爱  来吃饭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,今天天气特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要总是睡在床上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我把洗的衣服晾起来了  下午帮忙收回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:51.09,Top,,0,0,0,,呀  都已经这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此  我在那边是不死身  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈今天早上要开会  所以现在就得出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,午餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,该不会是晚上溜出去在外面被卷入什么事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  伤情怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,算是搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,钱包呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要保护多少人小糸才能复活？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,唯独这件事  我没法告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果同时保护多个人  那就会更快一点？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真是个贪婪的小笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要是没保护好  你也没法得救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  敌人也不全是那么容易对付
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟它们只是「视而不见」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一群乌合之众
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你的挚友一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在某个世界里变成了雕像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,除非她的朋友去到那个世界  不然她就永远那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃她也自杀了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面  我是大号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你左边的是小号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有别的客人先来了  你稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,诶  还有其他人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也一直很担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,身材好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,待续
